me.normanmaurer.niosmtp.delivery
Interface SMTPDeliveryFuture

All Superinterfaces:
Future<Iterator<DeliveryResult>>
All Known Implementing Classes:
SMTPDeliveryFutureImpl
public interface SMTPDeliveryFuture
extends Future<Iterator<DeliveryResult>>

A Future which allows to register SMTPDeliveryFutureListener and also make it possible to access the DeliveryResult objects in a blocking fashion.

Author:
Norman Maurer
